      <title>比尔·阿克曼（Bill Ackman</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/bill-ackman-calls-out-triple-levered-etfs-zero-day-options-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼（Bill Ackman）瞄准了两个蓬勃发展的市场，这是一日交易者所钟爱的市场：高度杠杆交易所交易的资金和零日股票合同已成为华尔街最热门的期权策略之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/bill-ackman-calls-out-triple-levered-etfs-zero-day-options-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 15:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
