      <title>尼日利亚是一个人，因为非洲坐着关税货币干预措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/-usd-ngn-nigeria-is-alone-as-africa-ignores-tariff-fanned-fx-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税颠覆市场和全球贸易，非洲国家并不急于支撑当地的货币并利用有限的外交储备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/-usd-ngn-nigeria-is-alone-as-africa-ignores-tariff-fanned-fx-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 12:41:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在通货膨胀率上涨，混合银行业绩的美国股票中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-stock-futures-gain-as-big-banks-kick-off-earnings-season</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者评估了新鲜的消费者情感数据，美国股票在周五的损益之间转移了损失，该数据显示了40多年来的近期通货膨胀估算的估计值最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/us-stock-futures-gain-as-big-banks-kick-off-earnings-season</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 11:24:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库突然在警告特朗普的警告时突然交易像风险的资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街的岩石固定安全性，美国国债债券在恐慌时期一直是投资者的第一次征收港口。他们在9/11的全球金融危机期间集会，即使在美国自己的信用等级也被削减时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-11/treasuries-suddenly-trade-like-risky-assets-in-warning-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Apr 2025 02:50:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着华尔街动荡的建设，美国资产重新下沉：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着加剧的美国 - 中国贸易争端威胁到经济和金融体系的动荡，美国资产席卷全面。股票消除了收益，加入了债券和美元的损失，因为担心外国投资者正在击败美国资产撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Apr 2025 22:39:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
